{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a Government manufacturing leadership forum for small and medium firms",
        "additional_details": "Small and medium manufacturers are currently facing an unprecedented number of challenges as a result of government policies and legislation:\r\n\r\n- Dealing with the logistics and supply chain issues from Brexit\r\n- Staff recruitment\r\n- Transitioning to Net Zero\r\n- Dealing with increasing pace of technology advancement adoption / Industry 4.0\r\n- Access to finance\r\n\r\nA manufacturing leadership forum focused on small and medium firms  with ministerial support is needed to help firms grow and build back better.",
        "background": "Create a dedicated manufacturing leadership forum for small and medium firms so Government can hear directly the voice of manufacturing at this critical time. The request would be for a forum made up of trade associations and manufacturing firms across all regions of the UK.",
